<div type="translation" source="bib:Ramachandran1992_01">
  	
  	<p n="1">The Lord who was the greatest of the Buddhas.</p>			
				
</div>
<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
 	
 	<p n="1">The foremost Lord Buddha.</p>
 	
 </div>
      	
<div type="commentary">
        
    <p><bibl><ptr target="bib:Ramachandran1954_01"/></bibl> (p. 92) comments thus: <quote>Here Śākyamuni Buddha’s relative importance to other previous Buddhas such as Dīpaṅkara, etc., is implied.</quote></p>
</div>
      	
